{"tid":2451821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊朗頻違反核協議 以新離心機提煉濃縮鈾","createTime":"2021-03-18T11:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T11:25:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53bc07c3a579d2241d4774adb2731c3fc5c3ebbd","tid":2451821,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"伊朗頻違反核協議 以新離心機提煉濃縮鈾<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E6%A0%B8%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%B0%E9%9B%A2%E5%BF%83%E6%A9%9F%E6%8F%90%E7%85%89%E6%BF%83%E7%B8%AE%E9%88%BE-065201660.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%2585%2589%25E6%25BF%2583%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E9%2588%25BE-065201660.html&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2YleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=e0935481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%A0%BB%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E6%A0%B8%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BB%A5%E6%96%B0%E9%9B%A2%E5%BF%83%E6%A9%9F%E6%8F%90%E7%85%89%E6%BF%83%E7%B8%AE%E9%88%BE-065201660.html</a><br />\n<br />\n伊朗再次利用濃縮鈾作為籌碼，對西方國家施壓。國際際原子能總署報告指出，伊朗開始利用先進的離心機，提煉濃縮鈾，再次違反2015年達成的核子協議。<br />\n<br />\n報告當中表示，伊朗已經對174台IR-4離心機，注入&quot;六氟化鈾&quot;氣體，也就是說將進行鈾濃縮提煉。伊朗也從去年開始，就陸續把三組不同機型的離心機，搬移到地下的燃料濃縮廠。這些動作都已經違反了先前達成的核子協議。有分析指出，伊朗近期不斷違反協議當中，對核子活動的限制，明顯是向美國總統拜登施壓。但恐怕因此造成反效果，有消息指出英國將針對伊朗，展開新一波制裁。"},{"pid":"83f369e07c31b1c6a38596813f554b21281a869e","tid":2451821,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"老人痴呆，世界大亂"},{"pid":"d3af4152aadafd5dca300e4b32bedb4b83611e04","tid":2451821,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"弊燈外國政策又嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f01a579d7294807f438680f5388191b5fd1e68b","tid":2451821,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"登仔一上位，所有牛鬼蛇神仆住出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae68860048867cec8da0469c6c9301a22bc298a9","tid":2451821,"uid":18012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f01a579d7294807f438680f5388191b5fd1e68b","tid":2451821,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"登仔一上位，所有牛鬼蛇神仆住出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"敗登自己咪牛鬼蛇神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b16d6dc08db6e518681bc773b114626988d44bc","tid":2451821,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b452f485c0ddf4899876d7e6da83e9bb19ab7e","tid":2451821,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"伊朗只係支那放出嚟既調兵離支之計"}]}